; Coverage test for filters.cc early return in create_post_from_amount
; When an equity balance has a zero-valued commodity (e.g., AAPL stock
; bought and sold completely), the create_post_from_amount skips it
; with an early return

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stock    10 AAPL @ $150
    Assets:Cash    $-1500

2024/02/01 Sell
    Assets:Stock    -10 AAPL @ $160
    Assets:Cash    $1600

test equity
2024/02/01 Opening Balances
    Assets:Cash                                 $100
    Equity:Opening Balances
end test
